---
layout: base.njk
title: "Occasions & véhicules d'occasion à Ivry-sur-Seine (94) | RED-K MOTORS"
description: "Petites annonces auto : occasions contrôlées, filtres par marque et budget. Achat, reprise et vente de véhicules avec RED-K MOTORS à Ivry-sur-Seine — pro ou particuliers."
pageKey: achat-revente
scripts:
  effects: false
  video: false
breadcrumb:
  "@context": "https://schema.org"
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList"
  itemListElement:
    - "@type": "ListItem"
      position: 1
      name: "Accueil"
      item: "https://redk-motors.me/"
    - "@type": "ListItem"
      position: 2
      name: "Achat & revente"
      item: "https://redk-motors.me/achat-revente/"
---

{% set heroActions %}
<a class="btn btn--primary" href="#annonces">Voir les annonces</a>
<a class="btn btn--secondary" href="/contact/">Vendre / reprendre mon véhicule</a>
{% endset %}


<section class="hero hero--subpage" aria-labelledby="achat-hero-title">
  <div class="hero__img-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/assets/img/achat-revente.jpg" alt="Occasions et achat-revente véhicules RED-K MOTORS" loading="eager" />
  </div>
  <div class="hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container hero__content">
    <div>
      <p class="hero__kicker">Petites annonces auto</p>
      <h1 id="achat-hero-title">Trouvez votre prochaine voiture près d'Ivry</h1>
      <p>Comme sur une marketplace auto : annonces détaillées, filtres par marque, carburant et budget. Toutes nos occasions passent par notre atelier.</p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        {{ heroActions | safe }}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="marketplace" id="annonces" aria-labelledby="marketplace-title">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="marketplace__intro">
      <h2 id="marketplace-title">Annonces véhicules</h2>
      <p class="marketplace__lede">
        Sélection d'occasions contrôlées. Une question sur un véhicule ? Contactez-nous par téléphone, formulaire ou WhatsApp depuis chaque fiche.
      </p>
      <div class="marketplace__sell-cta">
        <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact/">Proposer mon véhicule</a>
        <a class="btn marketplace__sell-tel" href="tel:{{ site.phone }}">Estimation au {{ site.phoneDisplay }}</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="marketplace__toolbar">
      <form class="marketplace__filters" action="javascript:void(0)" autocomplete="off">
        <div class="marketplace__field marketplace__field--search">
          <label class="sr-only" for="marketplace-search">Rechercher une annonce</label>
          <input type="search" id="marketplace-search" name="q" placeholder="Marque, modèle, mots-clés…" />
        </div>
        <div class="marketplace__field">
          <label class="sr-only" for="marketplace-brand">Marque</label>
          <select id="marketplace-brand" name="brand" aria-label="Filtrer par marque">
            <option value="">Toutes les marques</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="marketplace__field">
          <label class="sr-only" for="marketplace-fuel">Carburant</label>
          <select id="marketplace-fuel" name="fuel" aria-label="Filtrer par carburant">
            <option value="">Tous carburants</option>
            <option value="Essence">Essence</option>
            <option value="Diesel">Diesel</option>
            <option value="Hybride">Hybride</option>
            <option value="Électrique">Électrique</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="marketplace__field marketplace__field--price">
          <label class="sr-only" for="marketplace-price-max">Budget maximum</label>
          <input type="number" id="marketplace-price-max" name="price_max" min="0" step="500" placeholder="Budget max. (€)" inputmode="numeric" />
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="marketplace__reset" id="marketplace-reset">Réinitialiser</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <p class="marketplace__count" id="marketplace-empty" hidden>Aucun véhicule ne correspond à ces critères. Modifiez les filtres ou <a href="/contact/">demandez-nous une recherche</a>.</p>

    <div class="marketplace__grid" id="marketplace-grid">
      {% for listing in vehicleListings.listings %}
      <article
        class="marketplace-card"
        id="listing-{{ listing.id }}"
        data-listing
        data-brand="{{ listing.brand }}"
        data-fuel="{{ listing.fuel }}"
        data-price="{{ listing.price }}"
        data-title="{{ listing.title | e }}"
      >
        <a class="marketplace-card__media" href="{{ listing.image }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Voir la photo : {{ listing.title | e }}">
          <img src="{{ listing.image }}" alt="" loading="lazy" width="400" height="225" />
          {% if listing.highlight %}
          <span class="marketplace-card__badge">{{ listing.highlight }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
        <div class="marketplace-card__body">
          <p class="marketplace-card__price">{{ listing.price | formatFrNumber }}&nbsp;€</p>
          <h3 class="marketplace-card__title">{{ listing.title }}</h3>
          <ul class="marketplace-card__specs">
            <li><span class="marketplace-card__label">Année</span> {{ listing.year }}</li>
            <li><span class="marketplace-card__label">Kilom.</span> {{ listing.mileage | formatFrNumber }} km</li>
            <li><span class="marketplace-card__label">Énergie</span> {{ listing.fuel }}</li>
            <li><span class="marketplace-card__label">Boîte</span> {{ listing.transmission }}</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="marketplace-card__location">{{ listing.location }}</p>
          <div class="marketplace-card__actions">
            <a class="btn btn--primary marketplace-card__btn" href="https://wa.me/33648745668?text={{ ('Bonjour RED-K MOTORS, je souhaite des informations sur : ' ~ listing.title ~ ' — ' ~ (listing.price | formatFrNumber) ~ ' €. Merci.') | encodeURIComponent }}">WhatsApp</a>
            <a class="btn marketplace-card__btn marketplace-card__btn--outline" href="/contact/">Message</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="marketplace-trust" aria-labelledby="marketplace-trust-title">
  <div class="container marketplace-trust__inner">
    <h2 id="marketplace-trust-title">Pourquoi passer par RED-K MOTORS</h2>
    <ul class="marketplace-trust__list">
      <li>Véhicules présentés après contrôle en atelier</li>
      <li>Accompagnement reprise / financement sur demande</li>
      <li>Garage fixe à Ivry-sur-Seine — pas une annonce anonyme</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="/assets/js/marketplace.js" defer></script>
